   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3168_0038"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Austria</rs></hi>.</addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168934">IX. Frankga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 1</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3168_0039"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb118677">Singapore</rs></hi>, <date when="1898-04-27">27. <hi rend="latintype">April</hi></date>.</dateline></opener><p>Hier brennt die Tropen<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>onne erbarmungslo<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>er, als je, und ich bin fa<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t verrückt vor
               Hitze. <rs type="place" ref="#pmb1019">A<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ien</rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t eine<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elt<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ame Welt, aber wie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t es zu Hau<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e, in einem grünen <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40876">Wiener-Wald</rs>-Thale. Und alle Palmen von <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb118677">Singapore</rs></hi> gäbe ich um eines einzigen lieben Men<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen von daheim.</p><closer>Viele treue Grüße Dir u. <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard</rs></hi>.<lb/>Dein <signed>P. G.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
